@node "History" "History"


  @{FG shine}1.1@{FG text}   - first public version
  @{FG shine}1.41@{FG text}  - second public version
          - didn't show NewIcons tooltypes
          - you can read any icon
  @{FG shine}2.0@{FG text}   - rewritten program
          - you can disable/enable tooltype by clicking on it
          - you can save to any icon

  Lots of changes..

    4.0   - New GUI - now with tabs - you can configure all MV 4.x
    4.1   - Added sorting of lists
    4.4   - Added changing page via keys
    4.6   - Added datatype types
          - Added window blocking
          - When you add FileID types they are sorted
          - From now program checks is this type already exist
    4.7   - You can select listview position with UP/DOWN cursors.
    4.8   - Fixed error from 4.6 version - when you selected anything in
            filerequster then you have something different inserted into config

@endnode
@node "blabla" "BlaBlaInfo"

   @{b}@{fg shine}BlaBla@{ub}@{fg text} is a Polish biggest system programmers group. We make the system
friendly programms. We guarantee that our programs will run on almost every
machine (@{fg fill}Amiga@{fg text} of course), including future ones. All our programs are
running in multitasking, and all of them are PD, Freeware, or Shareware.

   Our organisation has a few members (we "absorb" only good programmers),
an own e-mail address. Our newest productions you can find in our PD library
called "@{b}Polware@{ub}". Our texts, articles you can also find in our
disk-mag "@{b}Izviestia@{ub}" (sorry, in Polish!).

   @{b}@{fg shine}BlaBla@{ub}@{fg text}  group  is  well-known  in Poland, and programs signed with
